metadata.name: Fractured Cells #30
metadata.description:
Poisson disc sampling of a noise field masked to a shape, and then Voronoi tessellation. Rendered in hand-drawn lines.

Press 's' to take a screenshot. The image size is 1000x1000. 

Features
- 48 curated possible palettes
- 4 possible color distribution methods
- 3 possible shapes: one circle, random circles, circles distributed based on a quadtree 
- 1 to 3 levels of polygon smoothing
- polygon outlines
- polygon fill density and direction
- hand-drawn line roughness

Rare features
- 1 circle
- no polygon smoothing
- background polygons offset from foreground
- color distribution to have a "striped" appearance

metadata.name: Layered Landscapes #59
metadata.description:
Layered Landscapes explores representing imaginary landscapes through line art designed for output with a pen plotter.

It supports these variations:

Hill Contours: 4 layers
Dark Foreground: 50% chance the first contour is overprinted for darker darks
Sky: straight or curved
fog: 0, 1 or 2 layers
trees: 1 to 7

Press "s" to download the SVG.

Output is designed for 6" x 4".

metadata.name: Top of Mountains #29
metadata.description:
Isn't the view beautiful on top of the mountains?

Sky, clouds, and mountains are generated with random dots, lines and shapes.
Made with p5.js.

Features:
1. Time: Day/Sunset/Night
2. Clouds: Yes/None
3. Light Source: Left/Right

Keys:
s: save the image as PNG
2: save the image in medium resolution 2000x2000
4: save the image in high resolution 4000x4000

When saving the image in medium/high resolutions, please note that it takes several seconds to redraw before the image is downloaded.

metadata.name: Gear for your quests - Sword #127
metadata.description:
Gear for your quests - Sword

Prepare for your quest, whatever it will be, taking one of these swords! (or more...you got more than one finger, right?)

Some will have power that could help you in your journey...

If you are lucky you could get a unique one!

Each unique sword was owned by a hero that you met, or by a boss you slayed, or maybe you found it in a distant region...who knows...

Legendary and uniques will be imbued two powers at the same time!

Some swords will have strange names, some will make no sense...maybe those are names inherited from bygone ages...

Item Rarity is split in 6 levels:
 - Common
 - Magic
 - Rare
 - Epic
 - Legendary
 - Unique

Each sword also has a "Purity" stat from "Tier 9" (the lowest) to "Tier 0" (with incredible purity, way above 90%)

I created this generator back in 2016 for my mobile game "Idle Duels" and improved it over these years
